('95431','32914','5','9 hole golf course with building permit for 5 Star Hotel'),
('95432','32915','5','To the north of Mallorca is this well-maintained 9-hole golf course on is built on a 240.000m² of land. More than 347.000m² are available around the golf courseto extand to 18 holes. A permit for a 5 star Golf Hotel with max. 50 rooms and club area is available. You are welcome to see in our office plans of the hotel project. The owner accepts only serious offers.\r\nAt the edge of the golf course is an exclusive villa park with 12 sold luxury villas. 15 villa plots, with a total of 21.300m², can still be purchased. The total price of the land is € 12 million. All plots are located on a hillside in south-west orientation and have a fantastic  panoramic view over the golf course and partially to the sea\r\n'),
